WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.840
Hi, my name is Shannon Pileggi. I'm a data scientist and I work in clinical trials

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:11.080
and I work in data all day long. However, today the talk I'm going to show you, I'm

00:00:11.080 --> 00:00:14.600
not going to show you any clinical trials data because I think what I'm

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:19.440
talking about is applicable to a wide audience and I want this talk to be

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:25.920
accessible to all. I'm going to start off by talking to you about a situation that

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:31.280
could happen in anyone's workplace, showcase the problems that that

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:35.959
situation highlights, some solutions to those problems, and extensions to that

