solution. And I know that today we are in the tables session and I just want to

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:44.880
get your brain oriented that we're like there's only a little bit of tables in

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:49.439
this talk. I'm really going to be talking to you about metadata, so close the door

00:00:49.439 --> 00:00:57.880
y'all are stuck with me now. All right, so the setting. You get an email. Hi Shannon,

00:00:57.880 --> 00:01:02.840
I see Travis is out on vacation. Can you rerun the flight delay report? Please

