data file sizes, if you know? I have no idea. That's a great question.

00:18:52.060 --> 00:18:54.619
Is there a way to attach data types as well?

00:18:54.939 --> 00:19:02.619
Attach? I mean, I think, yeah, that's a tough one. I feel like you could include it in the label.

